Usage: report_pg_keepout [-help] [-file <string>] [-cell <string> | -inst <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>     # specify cell name to report cell PG keepout(s).
                   # (string, optional)
-file <string>     # specify the file name to dump cell PG keepout(s).
                   # (string, optional)
-inst <string>     # specify inst name to report inst PG keepout(s)
                   # (string, optional)